HEADWORD: make-work
<hw>make-work</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Active work of litle value, such
as assignments given by teachers to students to keep them busy while the
teacher performs other tasks, or chores performed to while away time;
also called <altname>busywork</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> busywork.</syn>⟦br⟧
